52.7	White_Christmas_(song)	White Christmas (song)	"White Christmas" is an Irving Berlin song reminiscing about an old-fashioned Christmas setting. According to the Guinness Book of World Records, the version sung by Bing Crosby is the best-selling single of all time, with estimated sales in excess of 50 million copies worldwide.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/36/Single_Bing_Crosby_-_White_Christmas_cover.jpg/220px-Single_Bing_Crosby_-_White_Christmas_cover.jpg
